@startuml 05_Janus信令状态机
title Janus 信令状态机

[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Connecting : connect()
Connecting --> SocketOpen : onOpen
SocketOpen --> SessionCreating : createSession
SessionCreating --> SessionReady : success\nstartKeepAlive(10s)
SessionCreating --> ErrorState : 15s 超时\nINIT_FAILURE
SessionReady --> PluginAttaching : attachPlugin(videocall)
PluginAttaching --> PluginAttached : success → handleId
PluginAttaching --> ErrorState : 15s 超时
PluginAttached --> Registering : registerUser(localName)
Registering --> Registered : EVENT registered
Registering --> ErrorState : 15s 超时
Registered --> Calling : call(offer, remoteName)
Calling --> InCall : EVENT accepted + answer
InCall --> WebRTCUp : webrtcup
WebRTCUp --> MediaFlowing : media receiving:true
MediaFlowing --> Hangup : hangup / peer hangup
Hangup --> SessionDestroying : destroySession
SessionDestroying --> [*]
ErrorState --> [*]

note right of SocketOpen
  重连场景:
  _sessionId 已存在 → claim
  stat>1 → onSocketReopen
  → restartOffer + resumeAlive
end note
@enduml
